inet.ipaddr.format

Class IPAddressLargeDivision

  • java.lang.Object
    • inet.ipaddr.format.AddressDivisionBase
      • inet.ipaddr.format.IPAddressLargeDivision
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AddressItem, AddressStringDivision, IPAddressStringDivision, java.io.Serializable

    public class IPAddressLargeDivision
extends AddressDivisionBase
implements IPAddressStringDivision
    This class supports a segment of an arbitrary number of bits. For a bit count less than or equal to 63 bits, AddressDivision is a more efficient choice.
    See Also:
